openworkflow  (Apache-2.0)
====================================================================
Source: https://github.com/openworkflowdev/openworkflow
License: Apache-2.0 (see packages/openworkflow/LICENSE.md for the
         original text).

Thodare vendors openworkflow as `@thodare/openworkflow` so we can pin
a known-good revision and apply Thodare-specific patches. The vendored
copy lives at `packages/openworkflow/`. Significant changes from
upstream are listed in `packages/openworkflow/UPSTREAM.md`.

Per the Apache-2.0 license, the original copyright notices and the
license text are preserved in `packages/openworkflow/`. No claim is
made to authorship of upstream openworkflow code; modifications to it
by asyncdotengineering are clearly marked in commit history and in
UPSTREAM.md.


====================================================================
Other dependencies
====================================================================
Standard runtime dependencies (Hono, better-auth, postgres, pg, zod,
Astro, Starlight, openworkflow's own deps) keep their own licenses,
listed in each package.json. See `pnpm licenses list` in the root
workspace for a generated audit.
